🔲 Optimize Permission Middleware with Redis

- Cache role → permissions in Redis
  key: role:{roleId}
  value: ["VIEW_WORKSPACE", "CREATE_PROJECT"]

- On permission check:
  → Try Redis first
  → Fallback to DB if cache miss
  → Store in Redis

- Add expiry (1 hour)

- Invalidate cache when:
  → role permissions updated
  → role deleted

- Goal:
  → Avoid DB hit on every request
  → Improve performance & scalability